OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and sunny, and becoming
OL,6,Fvery hot, locally exceptionally hot
OL,7,Ftoday, with the potential for
OL,8,Ftemperatures to cause significant
OL,9,Fdisruption. Also feeling humid,
OL,10,Falthough onshore breezes will keep
OL,11,Fcoastal areas a little fresher.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDespite largely clear skies
OL,14,Fmany places will have another warm or
OL,15,Fvery warm night, especially in large
OL,16,Ftowns and cities, with the humid
OL,17,Fconditions persisting.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
