OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FSunny inland, with perhaps
OL,6,Fpatchy low cloud and mist reaching the
OL,7,Fcoast, especially northern coasts,
OL,8,FBecoming breezy with the easterly
OL,9,Fwinds keeping coastal areas cooler,
OL,10,Fhighest temperatures in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHot or
OL,13,Fvery hot Friday, thereafter
OL,14,Ftemperatures decreasing. Bright or
OL,15,Fsunny spells Friday and Saturday,
OL,16,Fchance of thunderstorms, mainly
OL,17,FSaturday night. Cloudier Sunday,
OL,18,Fpatchy light rain possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
